title: Gate: Jieitai Kanochi nite, Kaku Tatakaeri 2nd Season (GATE)
synopsis: Several months have passed since the infamous Ginza Incident, with tensions between the Empire and JSDF escalating in the vast and mysterious "Special Region" over peace negotiations. The greed and curiosity of the global powers have also begun to grow, as reports about the technological limitations of the magical realm's archaic civilizations come to light.
